all you've wished for is
to perish.

36
00:02:33,033 --> 00:02:35,267
The price that
Koo Chan-sung must pay

37
00:02:35,333 --> 00:02:36,467
for someone like you is unfair.

38
00:02:36,533 --> 00:02:38,966
It is unjust, and unreasonable.

39
00:02:42,333 --> 00:02:45,500
I tried to stop him,
but he took it on himself.

40
00:02:45,966 --> 00:02:48,267
You wicked thing!

41
00:02:48,333 --> 00:02:50,234
Yes, yes.

42
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:53,534
I'm bad and wicked for keeping him
by my side, despite it all.

43
