quivering like that.

50
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,200
It's you, isn't it? Chan-sung.

51
00:03:57,266 --> 00:03:58,334
Don't you remember me?

52
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:00,833
Your friend,
Seol Ji-won from Boston.

53
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:05,900
Right, Seol Ji-won. So it was you.

54
00:04:07,133 --> 00:04:08,267
What brings you here?

55
00:04:08,333 --> 00:04:09,900
Oh, you heard from Sanchez?

56
00:04:09,966 --> 00:04:11,633
Or maybe Mi-ra, perhaps?

57
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,534
No, someone else.

58
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:17,400
I was told you were back in Korea,

59
00:04:17,466 --> 00:04:19,366
but I'm surprised to see
that you're really here.

60
00:04:20,666 --> 00:04:21,800
Really?

61
