because you missed me.

62
00:04:34,933 --> 00:04:36,233
Why did you come here?

63
00:04:38,966 --> 00:04:41,434
I heard you were preparing to
go to law school.

64
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:42,534
Or that's no longer the case?

65
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:45,700
Did your father, who's a judge,
finally give up on you?

66
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,300
He didn't give up on me,
but he passed away.

67
00:04:49,366 --> 00:04:51,934
Now I'm just doing what I like
right here.

68
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,733
And what is it that
you're happily up to?

69
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,166
I see, wine!

70
00:05:07,433 --> 00:05:08,866
Do you have any good wines here?

71
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:15,233
Give me a glass.

72
00:05:16,666 --> 00:05:19,266
Sure, why not?

73
00:05:26,966 --> 00:05:29,367
Is that him?

74
00:05:29,433 --> 00:05:30,966
The person who killed you?

75
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:55,633
What are you doing here?

76
